{"title":"春消息","authors":["陆泰"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":2,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春消息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陆泰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨夜风雪紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催开村头梅；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝头群雀醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊问早行人是谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步声声碎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢笑阵阵甜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举目望——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群群肥担赛燕穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥担上大路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路积雪快融完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥水溅了一满身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸不觉冷心欲燃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥担翻过山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满崖青松把头点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半似称赞半似惊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大年腊月干劲添。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥担过小桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东去绿水睁大眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿水哪知社员心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有股暖流出胸间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥担挑下田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里麦海笑开眉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝阳有意染流金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恰似丰收粮垛堆。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}